reviewText: Orny is awesome. Got to see him live once, he was filling in for Jay Mohr and I will go see Orny ANY day over Jay. The audience won that day!!!

Be prepared to laugh..a lot. Orny's in your face comedy makes you sit back and think and then see
the world through his eyes in a different light! I recommend this to everyone! Gather all your friends and
pop this in the DVD player! Enjoy an evening of laughs!
